{"tid":2364541,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"中國流亡藝術家：巴丟草","createTime":"2021-01-13T05:29:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T15:54:10.000Z","uid":96799,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f90650aadd7bd07dd05382031837926c88213beb","tid":2364541,"uid":96799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T05:29:07.000Z","msg":"啱啱無意中睇到呢位畫家  巴丟草<br />\n<br />\n佢最出名的畫作   -  劉曉波與劉霞的愛情<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6Yr3xvX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6Yr3xvX.jpg&h=11a82375&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFROM維基：<br />\n劉曉波 逝世： 2017 年 7 月 13 日，中國瀋陽市中國醫科大學附屬第一醫院<br />\n<br />\n劉霞是詩人、畫家和攝影師，與丈夫劉曉波同為中國持不同政見者，在2010年劉曉波獲得諾貝爾獎後被中國政府軟禁至2018年7月10日獲准出境，現居德國柏林。 <br />\n<br />\n心好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2f66c5839be7474183fbda9ba0e424cf63bf69e","tid":2364541,"uid":96799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T05:32:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/StQ7Zdy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FStQ7Zdy.jpg&h=ceb048e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n楊舒平演講風波是指2017年5月21日馬里蘭大學學院市分校畢業典禮上，來自中國大陸昆明的留學生楊舒平在發表畢業演講時，以美國的學習、生活的自身經歷為主軸的演講，因提及在昆明『每次外出都必須戴口罩』，以及將中美之間的空氣、民主和言論自由作對比所引發的風波。<br />\n<br />\n演講內容由昆明、馬里蘭空氣質量的對比，從中美城市環境的差異，呼籲為「民主、自由」的清新空氣而奮鬥，最後表達「自由是氧氣，自由是激情，自由是愛」的觀點。此講演內容引起中國部分留學生、媒體和民眾的強烈反應，在難以預料的輿論壓力下，她在新浪微博上道歉。"},{"pid":"4ccbae8efff518a2027d2aa23ec0b370d0022aa5","tid":2364541,"uid":245713,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T05:32:53.000Z","msg":"佢啲取態有少少反香港"},{"pid":"1e0dbda64def2d852ad8bf099e931e61a9c86455","tid":2364541,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ccbae8efff518a2027d2aa23ec0b370d0022aa5","tid":2364541,"uid":245713,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T05:32:53.000Z","msg":"佢啲取態有少少反香港"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T05:36:01.000Z","msg":"佢係反香港"},{"pid":"b786783ba7e00b098892ba8bf621d81ddcd69ed9","tid":2364541,"uid":256837,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T05:37:30.000Z","msg":"佢話香港人歧視大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da9f544588d667e576dc3f072b427401e921d090","tid":2364541,"uid":19557,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T05:57:20.000Z","msg":"呢條柒頭上次果幅圖之後已經變過街老鼠"},{"pid":"ffd06b9de12328d7c2898363b17afe9093cf722b","tid":2364541,"uid":23832,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T06:03:57.000Z","msg":"有時敵人嘅敵人都未必係朋友<br />\n反中共唔代表會撐香港人<br />\n香港人要爭氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5276c85a9d8c99b440ddb37e2b47f0abfd28f910","tid":2364541,"uid":96799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da9f544588d667e576dc3f072b427401e921d090","tid":2364541,"uid":19557,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T05:57:20.000Z","msg":"呢條柒頭上次果幅圖之後已經變過街老鼠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T07:28:04.000Z","msg":"咁咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咩畫？？<br />\n等我研究下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a85437a389a04ffe64da7318d99163cfef2a89fe","tid":2364541,"uid":292987,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T07:55:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"020ae3fad8f793f365d166a85f3d132e6585ca48","tid":2364541,"uid":357030,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T07:57:00.000Z","msg":"呢條友好似反侵 冇記錯既話"},{"pid":"17ec2ff2bc4e4c3cc177db01d6763cf2327c3d85","tid":2364541,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T07:58:42.000Z","msg":"垃圾支那狗嚟"},{"pid":"423e324867d4178b0908f26909d46aeffaefabe6","tid":2364541,"uid":78046,"like":1,"d